OL,3,CWho are Hezbollah and why is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Israel-Hamas conflict?
OL,6,FHezbollah has blamed Israel for the
OL,7,Fattack on September 17 and said the
OL,8,Fcountry will "for sure get its just
OL,9,Fpunishment" for its "criminal
OL,10,Faggression". The Israeli military has
OL,11,Fdeclined to comment.
OL,13,FThis latest incident comes amid rising
OL,14,Ftensions between Israel and Hezbollah,
OL,15,Fwho have been exchanging fire across
OL,16,Fthe border since the October 7 attack
OL,17,Fby Hamas that triggered the war in
OL,18,FGaza.
