OL,3,CWho are Hezbollah and why is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Israel-Hamas conflict?
OL,6,FOn January 2, an apparent Israeli
OL,7,Fdrone strike hit an apartment in a
OL,8,Fbuilding in a Shiite district of
OL,9,FBeirut, killing Saleh Arouri, who was
OL,10,Fa founder of Hamas' military wing and
OL,11,Fhad headed up the group's presence in
OL,12,Fthe West Bank.
OL,14,FAlthough they often support each other
OL,15,Fin their sparring with Israel, the two
OL,16,Fgroups do have differences.
OL,18,FHezbollah is not a Palestinian
OL,19,Forganisation and is Shia Muslim
OL,20,Fwhereas Hamas and the vast majority of
OL,21,FPalestinians are Sunni Muslims.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
