OL,3,CWho are Hezbollah and why is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Israel-Hamas conflict?
OL,6,FIn a speech in November, the secretary
OL,7,Fgeneral of the group, Hassan
OL,8,FNasrallah, said Hezbollah is prepared
OL,9,Ffor all options, adding: "And we can
OL,10,Fresort to them at any time."
OL,12,FThe fighting would "not be limited" to
OL,13,Fthe scale seen so far, he said.
OL,15,FThere has been significant diplomatic
OL,16,Fpressure placed on Hezbollah and
OL,17,FLebanon to ensure the war between
OL,18,FHamas and Israel does not spread to
OL,19,Fnew fronts.
