OL,3,CWho are Hezbollah and why is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in the Israel-Hamas conflict?
OL,6,FFollowing the near simultaneous pager
OL,7,Fexplosions, Hezbollah said it holds
OL,8,Fthe "Israeli enemy fully responsible
OL,9,Ffor this criminal aggression that also
OL,10,Ftargeted civilians", adding that
OL,11,FIsrael will "for sure get its just
OL,12,Fpunishment".
OL,14,FThis implies the group is preparing to
OL,15,Fretaliate, but its not clear what form
OL,16,Fsuch an attack could take.
OL,18,FMuch depends on how Nasrallah - who
OL,19,Fhas led Hezbollah since an Israeli
OL,20,Fstrike killed his predecessor in 1992
OL,21,F- chooses to act.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
